Introduction

NouerA is a seven-member boy group under Nouer Entertainment and CHROMOSOME. Formed through KBS's reality survival show MAKE MATE 1, they made their debut on February 26, 2025 with the mini album Chapter: New Is Now.

Their group name is a combination of "nouer", the French for "to tie together", and "era", meaning that NouerA will be connecting eras through their music.

On December 9, NouerA unveiled the promotional time table for the pre-debut digital single "Mu", which was released on December 14th.

At the group's debut showcase, they revealed their fandom name as "NovA" which stands for "New Orbit Via Aurora"
